column5: In a week I'll be traveling up 502 to Wabigoon, but will have some time to kill. Does anyone have any suggestions or experiences fishing off of 502 on the way up? I just thought no better way to kill time than cast a few lures
I don't know, but I suggest that this might be a good resource to find one:https://mappingsupport.com/p2/gissur...da_vector_topoThere is an option for an aerial photo too.
I seem to remember someone posted quite a bit of information on this a year or two ago. Try some search words, you may find it.
